value: Breeding and Palearctic winter visitor, near shallow waters: breeds North Africa coast, Canary Is, Cape Verde Is; winters all S of Sahara except desert SW.
Estuaries, rivers, lakes, and extensive marshes (Tropical and Temperate zones).
